name: Shared Reflections
description:
This was the first photo I have captured that had 2 animals in it sharing the same space. This for me changed the way I look at photography as I uploaded this onto my computer. 
Looking at this photo time and time again, I can feel the connection that this image sparks.
For me photography wasn't just about freezing moments anymore, it was about capturing a continuous stream of life that one single image can give off every time eyes look at it.
